data.description: Located in one of Bay County's most prestigious neighborhoods. Great location on Panama City Beach. Inside the home features split bedroom plan, master bath with Whirlpool jacuzzi and double sink vanity and walk-in closet. The second bath offers 'Jack &Jill' with double sink. Kitchen overlooks the activity in the great room for an open floor plan. The grand foyer is tiled with a view of the fireplace, which is perfect for entertaining, along with a great formal dining room. This beautiful Palm Bay homehas one of the largest fenced back yards. This home is move in ready, call today for your private showing.
